and the annex has its
own meaning as well.

183
00:13:14,991 --> 00:13:18,094
Examples of foundations are: the
ninben which stands for a human,

184
00:13:18,095 --> 00:13:22,998
the sanzui which represents water,
and the kihen which stands for a tree.

185
00:13:22,999 --> 00:13:24,699
Now, here's a little quiz.

186
00:13:27,971 --> 00:13:31,541
The Jewel Seeds are ancient
treasures in our world.

187
00:13:34,344 --> 00:13:39,344
They originally were magical stones
that granted wishes for their holders,

188
00:13:39,382 --> 00:13:41,984
but their execution
of power is unstable.

189
00:13:41,985 --> 00:13:44,153
Just like last night, they go
out of control on their own.

190
00:13:44,154 --> 00:13:47,814
They can harm their environment
in their search for a valid user.

191
00:13:53,764 --> 00:13:57,233
Sometimes they go out of
control using the powers

192
00:13:57,234 --> 00:14:00,803
of mistaken executions by people or
animals that randomly find them.

193
00:14:00,804 --> 00:14:03,994
Why are such dangerous things
sitting around in my neighborhood?

194
00:14:05,375 --> 00:14:06,805
It's all my fault.

195
00:14:08,678 --> 00:14:11,838
Back where I came from, my job
is to excavate ancient ruins.

196
00:14:12,783 --> 00:14:16,652
And one day, I found them
in an ancient monument.

197
00:14:16,653 --> 00:14:20,389
I had asked the research group
to hold onto them.

198
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:22,158
However, the time-space
transporter carrying them

199
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:25,529
met either an accident or
some kind of artificial tragedy.

200
00:14:34,404 --> 00:14:38,504
Twenty-one Jewel Seeds were
dispersed all over this world.

201
00:14:40,143 --> 00:14:42,803
So far, I've been able to find only two.

202
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,520
So there's nineteen more?

203
00:14:47,117 --> 00:14:47,937
Rise!

204
00:14:52,556 --> 00:14:55,686
Isn't the balsam getting
much bigger now?

205
00:14:56,526 --> 00:14:57,986
How many centimeters tall is it?

206
00:15:00,430 --> 00:15:03,265
Wait? Hold on a second.

207
00:15:03,266 --> 00:15:05,100
Listening to that story,

208
00:15:05,101 --> 00:15:10,101
the Jewel Seeds getting dispersed
wasn't really your fault at all, Yuuno.

209
00:15:10,607 --> 00:15:14,643
But I was the one that found them,

210
00:15:14,644 --> 00:15:16,212
so I have to find them all,

211
00:15:16,213 --> 00:15:18,762
and return them to the
place where they belong.

212
00:15:20,317 --> 00:15:21,784
Just a little...

213
00:15:21,785 --> 00:15:26,125
Just a little, I think I understand
how you feel, Yuuno.

214
00:15:27,757 --> 00:15:30,306
Yuuno, you take things very seriously.

215
00:15:32,462 --> 00:15:34,096
Oh, that's right.

216
00:15:34,097 --> 00:15:37,533
Did you put up signs saying these
plants are under observation?

217
00:15:37,534 --> 00:15:39,902
It would be quite the problem
if someone plucked them out,

218
00:15:39,903 --> 00:15:41,363
thinking they were weeds!

219
00:15:42,873 --> 00:15:44,540
Oh, and of course, make sure to

220
00:15:44,541 --> 00:15:47,610
write your name and the date
you planted the seed on the sign.

221
00:15:47,611 --> 00:15:48,811
Well...

222
00:15:48,812 --> 00:15:53,812
I'm sorry I roped you into it
last night by having to save me.

223
00:15:54,184 --> 00:15:57,253
But all I want from here on
is a little bit of time to rest,

224
00:15:57,254 --> 00:15:59,804
until my magical powers
are back to full strength.

225
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:01,523
A week...

226
00:16:01,524 --> 00:16:04,293
No, five days should be enough
to get my powers back,

227
00:16:04,294 --> 00:16:05,284
so until then...

228
00:16:07,130 --> 00:16:08,910
When they come back,
what will you do?

229
00:16:10,233 --> 00:16:13,333
I'll go on my search for the
Jewel Seeds again, alone.

230
00:16:14,704 --> 00:16:16,438
I won't allow that.

231
00:16:16,439 --> 00:16:18,173
You won't allow it?!

232
00:16:18,174 --> 00:16:21,577
It's impossible for me to help you
during school and cram school,

233
00:16:21,578 --> 00:16:24,280
but other than that, I can help.

234
00:16:24,281 --> 00:16:27,300
But there will be dangerous times,
just like last night.

235
00:16:33,924 --> 00:16:36,191
I mean, I've gotten
to know you already,

236
00:16:36,192 --> 00:16:38,260
and I've heard your story.

237
00:16:38,261 --> 00:16:39,895
I can't just let you go.

238
00:16:39,896 --> 00:16:43,933
Besides, if something like last night
were to happen here often,

239
00:16:43,934 --> 00:16:46,334
it would trouble everyone
around us, right?

240
00:16:47,637 --> 00:16:52,207
Yuuno, you're all alone and have
nobody around to help you, right?

241
00:16:52,208 --> 00:16:55,747
It's lonely to be all by yourself.
So let me help you.

242
00:16:59,883 --> 00:17:02,251
If someone needs your help,

243
00:17:02,252 --> 00:17:05,220
and you have the power
to help them out,

244
00:17:05,221 --> 00:17:07,690
you shouldn't debate
whether to help or not.

245
00:17:07,691 --> 00:17:09,621
That's what Dad taught me.

246
00:17:15,365 --> 00:17:17,065
Yuuno, you're in trouble,

247
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:22,660
and I can help you out, right?
With the power of magic.

248
00:17:26,209 --> 00:17:27,409
Yeah...

249
00:17:27,410 --> 00:17:31,690
I'm not sure if I can be
a proper mage or not, but...

250
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:35,520
You're already a mage, Nanoha.

251
00:17:36,286 --> 00:17:39,288
I think you have much more
talent for it than I do.

252
00:17:39,289 --> 00:17:40,556
Really?

253
00:17:40,557 --> 00:17:43,359
I'm not really sure about that myself,

254
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:45,290
but for starters, please
teach me all sorts of things.

255
00:17:46,029 --> 00:17:46,879
Bye-bye!

256
00:17:48,264 --> 00:17:50,043
I'll do my best!

257
00:17:51,768 --> 00:17:53,908
Yeah... Thanks.

258
00:17:54,738 --> 00:17:57,706
Okay, I'm almost home now!

259
00:17:57,707 --> 00:18:00,197
For now, how about we have
some snacks together?

260
00:18:00,844 --> 00:18:02,924
Sure. Thanks.

261
00:18:04,314 --> 00:18:06,394
I wonder what today's snack will be?

262
00:18:18,261 --> 00:18:19,828
Excuse me...

263
00:18:19,829 --> 00:18:21,897
Yuuno, that thing just now...

264
00:18:21,898 --> 00:18:24,500
A new Jewel Seed has been executed!

265
00:18:24,501 --> 00:18:25,968
It's really close by!

266
00:18:25,969 --> 00:18:27,302
What should I do?

267
00:18:27,303 --> 00:18:30,406
Let's head over there together.
Please help me.

268
00:18:30,407 --> 00:18:31,367
Okay.

269
00:18:48,425 --> 00:18:50,426
Nanoha! Raging Heart!

270
00:18:50,427 --> 00:18:52,097
Okay!

271
00:19:02,005 --> 00:19:04,115
It's already taken in one
of the local creatures.

272
00:19:05,408 --> 00:19:06,428
What's going to happen?!

273
00:19:10,447 --> 00:19:12,496
It will be tougher, because
it has a physical body!

274
00:19:13,583 --> 00:19:15,393
It'll be all right, I think.

275
00:19:16,886 --> 00:19:17,755
Nanoha!

276
00:19:18,655 --> 00:19:20,145
Boot up the Raging Heart!

277
00:19:21,458 --> 00:19:22,748
How do I boot it?

278
00:19:26,463 --> 00:19:29,465
Start at "I am the one who has been
given a mission!" The boot password!

279
00:19:29,466 --> 00:19:30,226
What?!

280
00:19:32,035 --> 00:19:34,903
I can't remember such a long spell!

281
00:19:34,904 --> 00:19:36,972
I'll tell you again, so repeat after me!

282
00:19:36,973 --> 00:19:37,933
Got it!

283
00:19:50,753 --> 00:19:52,592
Raging Heart?

284
00:19:54,424 --> 00:19:56,358
Stand by ready.

285
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:57,228
Set up.

286
00:20:09,005 --> 00:20:11,965
She booted up the Raging Heart
without a password?!

287
00:20:15,612 --> 00:20:17,132
Nanoha, the protective armor!

288
00:20:18,748 --> 00:20:20,268
Barrier Jacket.

289
00:20:30,827 --> 00:20:31,757
Nanoha!

290
00:20:53,583 --> 00:20:55,863
Protect condition: all green.

291
00:21:00,456 --> 00:21:02,356
No damage dealt from that blow?

292
00:21:03,226 --> 00:21:07,196
Just as I thought, this girl has
an amazing amount of talent.

293
00:21:07,197 --> 00:21:10,599
Ouch... but it didn't hurt
enough to make me say it.

294
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:13,469
Let's see. I need to do
that sealing thing, right?

295
00:21:14,637 --> 00:21:17,506
Raging Heart, please?

296
00:21:17,507 --> 00:21:18,774
All right.

297
00:21:18,775 --> 00:21:20,825
Sealing Mode, set up.

298
00:21:36,593 --> 00:21:38,233
Stand by ready.

299
00:21:39,128 --> 00:21:40,896
Lyrical, magical...

300
00:21:40,897 --> 00:21:43,177
Jewel Seed, Serial 16...

301
00:21:44,567 --> 00:21:45,497
Seal!

302
00:21:47,136 --> 00:21:48,306
Sealing.

303
00:22:10,059 --> 00:22:11,899
Receipt: No. XVI.

304
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:15,564
Is this good enough?

305
00:22:15,565 --> 00:22:18,225
Yeabh, it couldn't have
been any better.

306
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:31,900
What? Did I trip and hit
my head or something?

307
00:22:41,791 --> 00:22:44,251
I guess this is where you say,
"Thanks for the hard work"?

308
00:22:45,094 --> 00:22:47,344
Yeah, that's right.

309
00:22:48,097 --> 00:22:52,167
The first long day after I,
Nanoha Takamachi,

310
00:22:52,168 --> 00:22:54,568
became a mage is about to end.

311
00:22:55,571 --> 00:23:00,208
About my new friend Yuuno...
About magic...

312
00:23:00,209 --> 00:23:03,145
About being uncertain, and
what I don't understand...

313
00:23:03,146 --> 00:23:05,286
All in all, there are lots of things.

314
00:23:06,015 --> 00:23:08,295
Come to think of it, I'm starving.

315
00:23:10,586 --> 00:23:14,276
For now, I think I just have to
do my best in all sorts of things.

316
00:23:26,135 --> 00:23:27,102
Make a little wish

317
00:23:27,103 --> 00:23:31,933
Even though at times
I'll trip or get lost

318
00:23:33,042 --> 00:23:42,891
Because you're with me, I can
continue to smile and be energetic

319
00:23:48,257 --> 00:23:53,257
Ah, going over the sea of
cellophane and over the forests

320
00:23:55,064 --> 00:23:58,767
Passing through the silver wind

321
00:23:58,768 --> 00:24:02,804
I was looking for something
neither of us had

322
00:24:02,805 --> 00:24:07,805
Ah, I was just crying
inside a diorama of a city

323
00:24:09,612 --> 00:24:14,612
Until I met that warm hand that
reached out to me that day

324
00:24:17,153 --> 00:24:22,153
Among the swaying days,
I felt a strong gaze

325
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:29,360
Hey, I finally, finally
found the secret key

326
00:24:32,735 --> 00:24:34,403
Make a little wish

327
00:24:34,404 --> 00:24:39,004
Collecting the lemon-colored
drops from the moon

328
00:24:40,309 --> 00:24:45,309
I want to keep a light shining on
the road that you travel down

329
00:24:47,383 --> 00:24:48,917
Make a little wish

330
00:24:48,918 --> 00:24:53,717
I wonder if there is something I
can do even though I'm so little

331
00:24:54,757 --> 00:25:05,197
Because you're with me, I can
continue to smile and be energetic

332
00:25:13,476 --> 00:25:17,879
This and that as a mage,
such and such as a magical girl...

333
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:22,851
I, Nanoha Takamachi, will do
my best with lots of energy!

334
00:25:22,852 --> 00:25:25,187
But problems are piled up
like a mountain!

335
00:25:25,188 --> 00:25:27,456
Next up is an incident so big
it involves the entire city?!

336
00:25:27,457 --> 00:25:29,424
Geez, it's so tough!

337
